Trustee_10.name: Mohammed Al-Farsi
Trustee_10.content: During the investment process, I demonstrated trustworthiness and pro-sociality by prioritizing transparency and fairness, proposing a profit-sharing plan that significantly benefitted the investor. This resulted in a successful investment with a 100% return, reflecting my competence in managing resources effectively. My reliable and responsible behavior has solidified my reputation as a trustworthy trustee, open to building collaborative relationships. Previous interactions are not documented as this is my first engagement.

Investor_15.name: Ahmed Hassan
Investor_15.content: As a first-time investor, Ahmed Hassan exhibited significant trust and openness by engaging in this investment opportunity. His willingness to invest a substantial amount and collaborate on the profit-sharing plan reflects a strong inclination toward fairness and mutual growth. His positive and proactive behavior lays a promising foundation for future collaborative ventures, contributing to a positive initial reputation.
